'''Sudan''' ke naga [[Lefasana|lefasaneng]] la [[Afrika]]. ''Sudan'' e bodikela ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Afrika Leboa]].

Ka bophara ba naga, Sudan ke naga ya pele ka bogolo [[Afrika]]. 

''Sudan'' e agišane le : 
* [[Egypt]] (leboa),
* [[Eritrea]] le [[Ethiopia]] (bohlabela), 
* [[Kenya]] le [[Uganda]] to the (borwa bohlabela), 
* [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]] le [[Central African Republic]] to the (borwa bodikela),
* [[Chad]] (bodikela),
* [[Libya]] to the (leboa bodikela).

